OL,5,G0435 Discovering: James Brown
OL,6,     FA fascinating look at the life and
OL,7,     Fcareer of James Brown. Dubbed 'the
OL,8,     FGodfather of Soul', he was one of
OL,9,     Fthe most iconic figures in music
OL,10,     Fup until his death in 2006. (S5,
OL,11,     Fep 13)
OL,12,G0500 Elvis Presley: Classic Albums
OL,13,     FElvis Presley: Film revealing how
OL,14,     Fthe King created his seminal debut
OL,15,     Falbum. Sam Phillips, Keith
OL,16,     FRichards and BB King are among
OL,17,     Fthose discussing the album and its
OL,18,     Ffar-reaching influence.
